    <item>
      <title>科宁的失败加剧了参议院共和党与特朗普总统的紧张关系。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/us/trump-cornyn-paxton-senate-republicans.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员们对特朗普总统向一位受人尊敬的前领导人发起攻击感到愤怒，他们认为这位前领导人是忠诚的共和党人。现在，特朗普面临着来自他自己心怀怨恨的队伍的抵制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/us/trump-cornyn-paxton-senate-republicans.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 21:57:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科宁在德克萨斯州决选中的失败凸显了特朗普对共和党的控制。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/us/politics/paxton-cornyn-texas-republican-primary.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员约翰·科宁 (John Cornyn) 以 28 个百分点的优势输给了他的 MAGA 挑战者肯·帕克斯顿 (Ken Paxton)。这是历史上表现不佳的表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/us/politics/paxton-cornyn-texas-republican-primary.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 21:37:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>即使美国和伊朗达成协议，黎巴嫩人也会接受长期战争</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/world/middleeast/lebaon-war-deal-iran-us.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着以色列和真主党在南部的冲突加剧，黎巴嫩很少有人相信结束更广泛战争的外交努力将为该国带来和平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/world/middleeast/lebaon-war-deal-iran-us.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 20:44:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为了与特朗普达成协议，伊朗希望解冻数十亿资金</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/world/middleeast/iran-frozen-funds-trump-deal.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这笔资金已成为谈判的症结所在，伊朗坚称，如果不释放资金，有意义的谈判就无法开始。]]></description>
