    <item>
      <title>政府分析发现，反映联营合同的利润率“膨胀”</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/us/politics/reflecting-pool-contractor-trump.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[获得修复这座问题地标建筑的无投标合同的公司收取 20% 的费用。内部记录显示，典型的利润率为 6% 至 12%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/us/politics/reflecting-pool-contractor-trump.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 18:42:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>会见选民，共和党人试图摆脱党内的困境</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/us/politics/mike-flood-gop-town-hall.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[内布拉斯加州众议员迈克·弗拉德 (Mike Flood) 在大多数共和党人投票结束很久之后仍在与选民会面。国会议员得出的结论是，这样做在政治上太危险了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/27/us/politics/mike-flood-gop-town-hall.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 18:16:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
